name: From the Gothic and Fantastic Novels to Realism in Quebec
description: A study of the first wave of fiction in the 1830 with the Gothic Novel, and its evolution through fantasy, folklore and Novel of the Land which spread from 1846 to 1945. [24L]
prerequisites: FRE280Y5 or a minimum grade of 77% in FSL406H5 or equivalent, FRE240H5, FRE241H5 (or FRE240Y5) or permission of the department.
